verbose_text: Compared with BC, the conventional 0.04-mg/cm 2 atelocollagen coat induced an abnormal increase in the expression of the ITGalpha2, alpha3, alpha5, alpha6, alphaV, beta1 and beta3, as well as DDR1, after 3 days of culture (XREF_FIG).
evidence: expression of the ITGalpha2, alpha3, alpha5, alpha6
